ly mind-bending report projecting that TV ad spending on the Ohio Senate ra=
ce alone will be in the $400 million range. That=E2=80=99s nearly half a bi=
llion dollars for a single Senate seat. But this matchup, between Democrat =
Sherrod Brown and Republican Bernie Moreno, still ranks second to the Monta=
na Senate race on the list of the political class=E2=80=99s down-ballot fix=
ations. Whichever party wins that race will probably control the Senate.

