bd12a ) to Routh in 2023, found him totally weird and untethered from reali=
ty. =E2=80=9CIt was clear he was in way over his head,=E2=80=9D Gibbons-Nef=
f wrote this week.

But the most
interesting reporting came from the Associated Press, which discovered Rout=
h=E2=80=99s self-published memoir on Amazon. The 300-page book, still avail=
able on Kindle, is called Ukraine=E2=80=99s Unwinnable War: The Fatal Flaw =
of Democracy, World Abandonment and the Global Citizen=E2=80=94Taiwan, Afgh=
anistan, North Korea and the End of Humanity. I have read it so you don=E2=
=80=99t have to.

