 style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf=
">spoke</a></u> to Routh in 2023, found him totally weird and untethered fr=
om reality. =E2=80=9CIt was clear he was in way over his head,=E2=80=9D Gib=
bons-Neff wrote this week.<br/><br/>But the most
interesting reporting came from the Associated Press, which discovered Rout=
h=E2=80=99s self-published memoir on Amazon. The 300-page book, still avail=
able on Kindle, is called <i>Ukraine=E2=80=99s Unwinnable War: The Fatal Fl=
